{"type": "article", "id": 24734, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-31T06:52:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 25624, "name": "Bonaldo"}, {"id": 25625, "name": "ModoLuce"}, {"id": 25626, "name": "Studio AUTORI"}, {"id": 25627, "name": "Hult Design"}, {"id": 25628, "name": "Mininch"}, {"id": 25629, "name": "Roberto Paoli"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110324YkIis45uo3vzLKWb.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>STRUCTURE SOFA by Alain Gilles &amp; Bonaldo</h2>\n<p>这是比利时设计师 Alain Gilles 为意大利家居品牌 Bonaldo 设计的沙发，他认为沙发是从一个纸盒子里变化出来的，经过切割调整，再安装上金属结构。这组沙发就有着方正的轮廓，下面的腿非常纤细，通过体量的对比突出沙发本身的宽大，也能让人感受到舒适，<a href=\"http://www.alaingilles.com/en/project/52/structure-sofa\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182121NOz3UPXMlupY160K.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182122BlSP9JqGrcAg61Mi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071821227PiZtQOSRcvI1XeF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182123vsFptlnieC8rHLUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182123Q9CfAkxRZUJc12rt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Abc lamps by ModoLuce &amp;Roberto Paoli </h2>\n<p>这是意大利设计师 Roberto Paoli 为灯具品牌 ModoLuce 设计的吊灯，他使用了非常简洁的圆锥形。三种吊灯的开合角度不一样，拼凑在一起却增加了活泼的气氛。圆锥灯罩的上面横着放一个圆片，从侧面看就像是一条短的直线，隐隐与下面的圆锥构成了一种平衡，突出了吊灯本身的几何感。有 6 种颜色选择，<a href=\"http://www.modoluce.com/#/collezioni/sospensione/201601\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182124yvRd0WbDJxAPncNE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182124TCIkf3eY5xbWoFsr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182125ZsNdFugjYMntw2J4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182125KIh0d9rEBLROXNMD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23919308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Rotating table by Studio AUTORI</h2>\n<p>这张超长的桌子原本是为一个工作室打造的，来自塞尔维亚的设计团队Studio AUTORI 。它的一头是固定的，用白色的钢架支撑，对应的桌面可以接上了一个水池，而桌子的中间和另一头则装上了滚轮，可以绕着固定的一头旋转，很灵活。对于较大的工作间里的操作台是一个参考。<a href=\"http://autori.rs/en/roto/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182126BdKoqQRmPFJb08yA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182126MEjfwY453ckQoHbG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182127xWVDS1mYOTZ5ci74.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182127qd5ElgfXpeUxzhO4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182128EMct14PSTOqGZ5lk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75607181\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<h2>Pavilion Wireless Speakers by Hult Design</h2>\n<p>这款蓝牙音响用了多种材料，下面是混凝土底座，中间一层有黄铜丝，而在音响上面还有一层木头，很现代。设计师将它取名为“Pavilion”，意为凉亭，以呼应其中使用的常见于建筑的材料。黄铜丝的一段让底座和扬声器略有分开，让它有点像一个话筒。有黑白两色，售价 339 美元，<a href=\"https://hultdesign.com/?variant=13961169924\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182129WmN2prf79KEGT5oX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182129PoRgvhZjLxzH4kfJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182130VKli78qL5htwdpJP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071821303qk28CjT4mg7QEZv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071821309bjv4i1mSBxl7QVy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>THE TOOL PEN  by Mininch</h2>\n<p>这是台湾设计团队 Mininch 新推出的一个扳手，它的外形像一把尺子或者刀片。工具里面可以放 5 个可替换的拱形模块，上面有不同大小的六角形空缺或者其他形状的空缺来拧螺丝，以替代原本非常笨重的扳手，也方便携带。它一共有 10 种模块替换，目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2054052511/wrenchit-turning-smart\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182131zJcSjL4Exbaq65DR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182131jnJ4BNiscbrWzY8e.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6247619\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182133Y0dmRxNtbfA2D4yi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182134WHPB9E2GJ8Fwltgn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182134R6SMWCbK2AhjEDLT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182135AySdzrvpO3RqYoMk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Molocow package concept</h2>\n<p>这个牛奶瓶包装模拟了 UFO 吸走牛的场景，也有洗手液利用了同样的设计。塑料瓶盖是宇宙飞船的形状，通过银色增加未来感，而瓶身是圆锥形的，模拟了光束发散的形状，在瓶子中间画出了黑色的奶牛的图像和光点，似乎马上就要吸走牛了，很有故事。至少对于特别需要喝牛奶的儿童或青少年来说很有吸引力。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182135oX9S1Uwufyx5mqQk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060718213613GKo4FEivWlQMTj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182136EHwrGhxSl9ejCMvV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182137gt7yN32RSXZxfjEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182137UTJWx3a6rkYen5fm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}